Model type: 1. all these models' response variable is post relapse while persistent
2. interaction between treatment and other covariates were included in logistic regression model

4. modified outcome means label outcome as 1 if relapse and 0 if not for Gilenya; while code 0 if relapse and 1 if not for Tecfidera
5. the above results are on the basis of test data (50% of full data)
